OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FAs if the King's state visit to the
OL,7,FUSA this week didn't have enough
OL,8,Friding on it, there is now a security
OL,9,Freview underway before King Charles
OL,10,Fand Queen Camilla touch down in
OL,11,FWashington on Monday.
OL,13,FThe events at the gala dinner on
OL,14,FSaturday night have led to what
OL,15,FBuckingham Palace called "a number of
OL,16,Fdiscussions" taking place between
OL,17,Fthose in charge of security for the UK
OL,18,Fand the US sides.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
