CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FThe much-anticipated state visit is
OL,7,Fhappening at a time of tense relations
OL,8,Fbetween the two countries after Donald
OL,9,FTrump launched the war in Iran and has
OL,10,Frepeatedly lashed out at the British
OL,11,FPrime Minister for not supporting the
OL,12,FUS/Israeli offensive.
OL,14,FBoth the King and Queen have been in
OL,15,Ftouch privately with the President and
OL,16,FFirst Lady since they were evacuated
OL,17,Ffrom the Hilton hotel in Washington DC
OL,18,Fafter a suspected shooter managed to
OL,19,Fget passed the first ring of security.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FIn Washington, Charles and Camilla are
OL,7,Fdue to base themselves at Blair House
OL,8,Ffor the duration of their stay, which
OL,9,Fis close to the White House.
OL,11,FKing Charles is scheduled to have five
OL,12,Fface-to-face meetings over the four-
OL,13,Fday official visit, which is the first
OL,14,Fstate visit the White House has hosted
OL,15,Fsince the start of the second Trump
OL,16,Fadministration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Buckingham Palace
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement: "His Majesty is
OL,8,Fbeing kept fully informed of
OL,9,Fdevelopments and is greatly relieved
OL,10,Fto hear that the President, First Lady
OL,11,Fand all guests have been unharmed.
OL,13,F"As you would expect, a number of
OL,14,Fdiscussions will be taking place
OL,15,Fthroughout the day to discuss with US
OL,16,Fcolleagues and our respective teams to
OL,17,Fwhat degree the events of Saturday
OL,18,Fevening may or may not impact on the
OL,19,Foperational planning for the Visit,"
OL,20,Fthe palace statement concluded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FBut this week's trip comes at a time
OL,7,Fwhen the US President has been
OL,8,Fpersistently mocking the state of the
OL,9,FBritish military and the Royal Navy's
OL,10,Fcapabilities.
OL,12,FWhat he might not know, or hasn't been
OL,13,Finformed, is that members of the UK
OL,14,Farmed forces swear an allegiance to
OL,15,Fthe Monarch and therefore Trump is
OL,16,Findirectly offending the King, who is
OL,17,Fthe nominal head of the British
OL,18,Fmilitary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FKing Charles will meet Trump as one
OL,7,FHead of State to another, but the
OL,8,Fcrucial difference is that the British
OL,9,FMonarch does not hold executive power
OL,10,Fand is not in charge of government
OL,11,Fdecisions.
OL,13,FBut Downing Street has concluded the
OL,14,Frisk is worth taking and has kept the
OL,15,Fstate visit on track, despite the
OL,16,Fstrain in relations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FIt is the British government which
OL,7,Fdecides on the King's official visits
OL,8,Foverseas based on its priorities, so
OL,9,Fthe decision to cancel never rested
OL,10,Fwith Charles himself.
OL,12,FSo, he is doing what he has been asked
OL,13,Fto do by Sir Keir Starmer and meet
OL,14,Fwith President Trump to hold talks on
OL,15,Fa level no prime minister could
OL,16,Fachieve.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FBut despite the already high-stakes
OL,7,Fvisit, it is now taking place against
OL,8,Fthe backdrop of a security review
OL,9,Fafter Donald Trump and other top White
OL,10,FHouse officials were evacuated from
OL,11,Fthe annual dinner of the White House
OL,12,FCorrespondents' Association on
OL,13,FSaturday.
OL,15,FSenior Palace aides are braced for an
OL,16,Funpredictable week. Royal planners
OL,17,Fhave stripped out as much jeopardy as
OL,18,Fthey could.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FThere will be no TV cameras inside the
OL,7,FOval Office for example when King
OL,8,FCharles and President Trump hold their
OL,9,Fbilateral meeting, so reporters can't
OL,10,Fshout potentially awkward questions in
OL,11,Ffront of the King.
OL,13,FBut no one can predict what Trump
OL,14,Fmight do or say in his speeches or on
OL,15,Fsocial media during the 4 days when
OL,16,Fthe King and Queen are in the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
