FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FA source who is very close to the King
OL,7,Ftold ITV News last week, "if anyone
OL,8,Fcan talk some sense into President
OL,9,FTrump" then King Charles "can", they
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FAnd yet, despite hosting President
OL,13,FTrump for a second "unprecedented"
OL,14,Fstate visit in the UK last year, it
OL,15,Fhasn't stopped Trump talking
OL,16,Fnegatively - and very publicly - about
OL,17,Fthe British Prime Minister and UK
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUqD@FO]qD@ZOUqD@^O]uD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
