CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FThe White House has said that First
OL,7,FLady Melania Trump "led the
OL,8,Fpreparations for the state visit,
OL,9,Fwhich will honour the longstanding and
OL,10,Fspecial relationship between the
OL,11,FUnited States and the United Kingdom
OL,12,Fas the American people mark 250 years
OL,13,Fof independence."
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@uD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FAnd whatever the political temperature
OL,7,Fat this time, which is decidedly cold,
OL,8,Froyal officials keep pointing to the
OL,9,Fimportance of marking the big quarter
OL,10,Fof a century moment of American
OL,11,Findependence.
OL,13,FAfter flying into Washington on Monday
OL,14,Fafternoon, the King and Queen will
OL,15,Farrive at the South Portico of the
OL,16,FWhite House.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FThe President and First Lady will take
OL,7,Ftheir guests "to the State Floor where
OL,8,Fthey will sit for tea in the Green
OL,9,FRoom" according to a White House
OL,10,Fstatement.
OL,12,FThey will also get a tour of the
OL,13,F"newly unveiled and expanded White
OL,14,FHouse Beehive" on the South Lawn which
OL,15,Fis likely to interest the King and
OL,16,FQueen much more than Trump, given King
OL,17,FCharles' interest in nature and
OL,18,Fbiodiversity.
OL,26,@qD@EO]vD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777291867
OL,3,CReview of security underway ahead of
OL,4,Cthe King's high-stakes visit to US
OL,6,FBut that beehive visit is no guarantee
OL,7,Fthere won't be a sting in the tail for
OL,8,Fthe British at some point during this
OL,9,Fofficial trip.
OL,11,FUK diplomats and senior royals, in
OL,12,Fboth London and Washington DC, are
OL,13,Fholding their collective breath.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
